		<title>AFP Keeps Pressure on Lawmakers, Encouraging Congress to Pass Right-to-Try Legislation</title>
		<link>https://americansforprosperity.org/afp-keeps-pressure-on-lawmakers-encouraging-congress-to-pass-right-to-try-legislation/</link>
